OL,3,CYounger workers in England face 'place-
OL,4,Cbased' pay penalty, study warns
OL,6,FThis leads to a full-time worker early
OL,7,Fon in their career suffering a 5%
OL,8,F"place-based pay penalty", according
OL,9,Fto the think tank. This could be worth
OL,10,Fabout #1,300 year if they move from a
OL,11,Ftypical high-paying jobs market, such
OL,12,Fas Harrogate, to a low-paying one,
OL,13,Fsuch as Dudley.
OL,15,FThe study analysed earnings data
OL,16,Fspanning all early-career workers in
OL,17,FEngland, covering more than 11 million
OL,18,Findividuals.
