OL,3,CYounger workers in England face 'place-
OL,4,Cbased' pay penalty, study warns
OL,6,FThe Resolution Foundation said
OL,7,Fpolicymakers can address the issues by
OL,8,Fencouraging housebuilding, including
OL,9,Faffordable homes, in better-paying
OL,10,Fareas, and supporting higher-paying
OL,11,Ffirms to expand to regions across
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FGreg Thwaite, research director at the
OL,15,FResolution Foundation, said: "England
OL,16,Fis beset by stark and persistent
OL,17,Fgeographic wage inequalities, with
OL,18,FLondoners' typical earnings twice as
OL,19,Fmuch as those living in places like
OL,20,FLiskeard or Cromer.
